{"word":"G2839 - κοινός - koinós - koy-nos' - Common","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κοινός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">koinós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">koy-nos'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Common</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அசுத்த, தீட்டுள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"common, defiled, unclean, unholy"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Probably from <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a>; <i>common</i>, that is, (literally) shared by all or several, or (ceremonially) <i>profane:</i> - common, defiled, unclean, unholy.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2839/2839\">G2839</a>, <a href=\"#/G2840/2840\">G2840</a>, <a href=\"#/G2841/2841\">G2841</a>, <a href=\"#/G2842/2842\">G2842</a>, <a href=\"#/G2843/2843\">G2843</a>, <a href=\"#/G2844/2844\">G2844</a>, <a href=\"#/G4790/4790\">G4790</a>, <a href=\"#/G4791/4791\">G4791</a>"}]}